<div class="menu-panel-bbs">The ACLU works tirelessly in courts, legislatures, and communities to defend and preserve the Constitution’s promise of liberty for everyone in our country.</div>
</div></div></div></li>
<li class="menu__item is-expanded expanded"><span id="main_menu-blogs" class="menu__link aclu_menu_expand-images nolink">Blogs</span><div class="menu-panel"><div class="inner"><div class="inner-inner">
<div class="menu-panel-container">
